description:

Our subconscious mind is infinitely more powerful than our conscious minds. It holds the key to manifestation, and the Elites are smart enough to target the subconscious' of the masses to get them to manifest their reality. Stop watching television, stop watching mainstream Netflix series, stop watching movies, stop watching/reading/listening to maintainstream news. All of them are designed to alter your subconscious mind. You should instead envision your desired ideal reality. Practice visualizations, affirmations, and most importantly meditate daily. These are some of the the most beneficial and power practices we can do as human beings. The Elites don't want you to know that. But I do :)
